Package: metadidsims
Title: Simulation Validation Studies for the metadid Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ben", "Lambert", email = "ben.c.lambert@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Internal repository of simulation-based validation studies
    for the metadid R package. Not intended to be installed as a package;
    this DESCRIPTION exists so that GitHub Actions
    (r-lib/actions/setup-r-dependencies) can resolve and install every R
    dependency of the targets pipeline and the Quarto validation report
    from a single source of truth, eliminating drift between code and CI.
